original_title: 20年間北国育ち─ 無垢な天然もち肌ガールがAVアイドルを夢見て、ひとり東京にやってきた。AV初出演！ 春日えな（仮）20歳
overview: After graduating from school, 20-year-old Ena-chan dreamed of becoming vaguely famous. She has a part-time job, but she doesn't feel right. One day she saw an AV recruitment ad and she applied that this was the only way she could become famous. She later went to Tokyo and took a test squirrel and took her first shot at her hotel. While being blown by the tide with toys, it's so exciting that it's hard to believe it's the first time!
title: Raised Up In The North For 20 Years -- Innocent Naturally Curvy Girl Dreaming Of Becoming An AV Idol Who Comes To Tokyo Alone. First AV Appearance! Ena Kasuga (20), Provisional.
